Task2:
    
Get two strings from user  example: 
    "java" "groovy" ==> java6groovy4
   
   "pi" "mathematics"  ===> pi15mathematics2
   
   
 Code:
   
   
x= input("Enter the String1:\n")
a= len(x)
y=input("Enter the String2:\n")
b= len(y)

print("Result of String is {}{}{}{}".format(x,b,y,a))


   
